<v-dialog v-model="dialog" max-width="500">
  <template v-slot:activator="{ on }">
    <v-btn v-on="on" small color="#003b94" dark> Status </v-btn>
  </template>
  <v-card>
    <v-form ref="form" v-model="valid" v-on:submit.prevent="Cambiar(id)" lazy-validation>
      <v-toolbar dark color="indigo">
        <v-toolbar-title >Actualizar status de compra</v-toolbar-title>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      </v-toolbar>
      <v-layout row>
        <v-flex xs10 offset-xs1 >
          <v-select
            class = "purple-input"
            label = "Status de la compra"
            name = "status"
            :value = "status"
            :items = "items"
            id = "estado"
            outlined
          />
        </v-flex>
      </v-layout>
      <v-card-actions>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <v-btn
          color="green darken-1"
          flat="flat"
          @click="dialog = false"
        >
          Cancelar
        </v-btn>

        <v-btn
          color="green darken-1"
          flat="flat"
          type="submit"
          @click="dialog = false"
        >
          Actualizar
        </v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-form>
  </v-card>
</v-dialog>
